high_descs: Step to the left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the kitchen table.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the tomato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and look up to face the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato slice plus place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the left of the sink
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn around and go to the table
Slice the tomato on the table
Put the knife on the table
Grab a slice of the tomato
Turn right and go to the fridge
Cool the tomato slice in the fridge and then take it out
Turn right and go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold tomato slice in the microwave

high_descs: Move over left to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife on near the edge of the counter.
Turn around and go to the white table across the room.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Place the knife on the right side of the table.
Pick up one slice of the tomato from the table.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato slice in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn right and go to the microwave above the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato slice in the microwave.
